formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1	Sale value of the unsold property taken as certify by the management.
2	Estimated construction value of the project taken as certify by the engineer.
3	Technical measurement taken as provided by the management.
4	Actual cost taken as per books of accounts up to 31.01.2022
5	Amount mentioned at point ii sub clause c for interest payable includes amount paid for stamp duty and franking charges for Loan taken from SBI Bank. 
6	The details mentioned at column Allotee name, Type of KYC, KYC ID and Mobile Number is taken as certified by the management.
7	The details mentioned at secured loan is in nature of C/C account and accordingly repayment has been adjusted as per closing balance of the loan. The actual ledger has also been enclosed. 
8	70% withdrawal amount at point 7 is worked out as 70% of total collection received till date since 70% RERA account is also utilized for payment to creditors and others.
9	Some of the Onsite Expenditure has been re-bifurcated to Cost of Construction and accordingly onsite expenditure has been reduced to that extent.
